{"tid":83323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶］試食新鮮炸烏龜","createTime":"2017-01-16T15:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T18:11:59.000Z","uid":4550,"like":13,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6471bbd06618973d1bd32e6d7fcda98516a84eb1","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:50:05.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「好喇，我哋而家示範如何將炸咗嘅龜切開嚟食」。近日有人在互聯網上載一段懷疑殘殺烏龜的短片，片段中一名相信是小學生的男童仿效煮食節目主持的口脗作旁述，以刀叉將一隻疑被炸過的烏龜分屍，激起網民狠批。原來上載者除炸龜外，亦曾將食糧黐在龜殼上餵食天竺鼠。有心理學家形容事主行為變態；警方表示會了解事件。<br />\n日前有人在互聯網上載一段題為「試食新鮮炸烏龜」的短片，片長逾兩分鐘，只見一隻小烏龜被放在碗中毫無反應，龜板呈金啡色疑被炸過。<br />\n旁述是一把細路仔聲音，他隨後持刀叉手起刀落，揚言示範食炸龜。「切咗個頭先，拮住個頭」烏龜頭部慘被切開，旁述更以非常鬆脆來形容。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120619/large/19la9p1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120619%2Flarge%2F19la9p1n.jpg&h=ad254612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上流傳短片，男童旁述示範如何將炸龜切開。<br />\n互聯網<br />\n糧放殼上任天竺鼠啄<br />\n然後事主猛力又敲又拮龜殼，「由於炸咗好耐嘅關係，成個殼已經俾我拮穿咗&hellip;&hellip;分屍，嘩，條腸呀，超核突的！」他將龜身連殼一分為二，血肉相連，慘不忍睹。片段引起網民群起鬧爆：「有冇人性呀你！」除此之外，原來該名上載者已非第一次虐龜，炸烏龜片段上載前一日，他曾上載另一條名為「與天竺鼠聯合虐待小龜！超爽的！」片段，他將天竺鼠的乾糧黐在龜殼上，讓兩隻天竺鼠圍住龜殼啄食。<br />\n<br />\n專家：需接受適當輔導<br />\n其間，片段中出現一把成年婦人的聲音，她似剛從外返家，帶笑說：「嘩，你玩死咗佢（龜）呀？你黐線㗎你？哎吔，你玩死隻龜囉！」豈料，事主竟大言不慚回應：「隻龜死咗唔緊要。」然後又用網球扑打龜殼，甚至將龜殼當波踢。<br />\n臨床心理學家葉妙妍估計事主的行為有三個原因；第一，片段中的小朋友可能曾被虐待或欺凌，將不滿發洩在比自己弱小及無反抗能力的動物身上，有變態的心態；其次，事主性格反叛作出反社會行為，對人及動物殘忍，有人格失常的傾向；此外，事主將片段放上網欲引人注意，不在乎別人的批評；以為網上身份隱藏，不用承擔後果。葉認為，事主需要接受適當的輔導，以免長大後變成社會的危險人物。<br />\n愛護動物協會公關及傳訊經理顏綺苓表示，愛協已聯同警方跟進事件及追尋片段源頭。顏綺苓稱，除非烏龜屬受保護的稀有品種，否則食用烏龜或將之餵飼其他動物不屬違法。"},{"pid":"fef1a361d25628bc2d5bc8dbbc36e3c928c90cba","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf6d91780878578632d48aca34bfb7a4c1debae","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"邊個正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58742f0981f331394d55e5e39607fb12f365cb88","tid":83323,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"非常鬆脆"},{"pid":"4fb7476cbe53c96ac0d35b577216bc0d58b3a9d5","tid":83323,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ae1879d9ebb306eebd6da66b8255e615bf71f04","tid":83323,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"第一句有聲<br />\n仲好記得個語氣"},{"pid":"2603a84dcb22fa4e7bc0868c37c9726e3b28e41c","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓我覺得好撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0d8314547176b2b48ff663fdadfe7b0c926a084","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吓我覺得好撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有佢係玩弄生命<br />\n而我地平時要食肉都係生活所需<br />\n個出發點都唔同"},{"pid":"aa3957d920487ca5894b86b54a5ef936f49166fb","tid":83323,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會食肉，並尊重所有成為我食物既生命，唔會浪費。<br />\n而片中條友係玩弄緊生命，製造無意義既死亡。"},{"pid":"af79a5aaa0b05da232f922ea7477e7ccada001cc","tid":83323,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20步屌100步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好嘔心"},{"pid":"872f6150bcc7e2e7b3ebd365aa50c71d5169b7ed","tid":83323,"uid":53368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"如果佢真係正正經經炸嚟食又有無問題呢"},{"pid":"9747821aebfc2f64dfdba06b203202f924d13eb6","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n20步屌100步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好嘔心</blockquote><br />\n已經唔關食唔食肉事<br />\n係佢虐待動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ba91875a6768583d9a4edaa0582360b6ff117c","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab3c9cb1d2ef1a11ff5ce38e48d8c846f5a4257","tid":83323,"uid":47084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"原來佢係真係冇犯法㗎？"},{"pid":"343c121fdc8ef981dbd60cbdacdaeaeb146904cf","tid":83323,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非常鬆脆</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd7869b88cbb482710d9fda293a57f77ad9ccd8","tid":83323,"uid":10671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢真係正正經經炸嚟食又有無問題呢</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦 恕我孤陋寡聞未見過有個菜式叫炸烏龜lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60c0dd67858ac6c7b2f7e977fba2f3959b7267","tid":83323,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NKMxGwHA7j4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNKMxGwHA7j4&d=98Zz%2Fi4ZD3yOQwlUZy72BWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7c572580\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NKMxGwHA7j4</a>"},{"pid":"a0d874389dc257eb36eafd4ea0cb2d144b37bfd9","tid":83323,"uid":51269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"記得以前有個網友話識佢，條友去左英國同埋有女"},{"pid":"839ed52a59a8179af9dff1cfa3a7e84dbb1416d2","tid":83323,"uid":10531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會食肉，並尊重所有成為我食物既生命，唔會浪費。<br />\n而片中條友係玩弄緊生命，製造無意義既死亡。</blockquote><br />\n如果隻牛/豬果類 正常用來食既動物<br />\n就算你唔食 佢都要死 咁咪令佢死得有價值 始終都係食物鏈會發生既野<br />\n<br />\n但隻龜本身唔係用黎咁用 同埋佢無食"},{"pid":"7a69d07cfbbb18b703baa3c87e3cbb666b57cbd7","tid":83323,"uid":17310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"Old news is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"a62fb7f11bcc43dbbe7c23258e790ea6d90c401b","tid":83323,"uid":57049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>非常鬆脆</blockquote><br />\n有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有最後句oh no仲係個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dfca5f93775db07aa6d0f2103da62173b10ad7","tid":83323,"uid":6571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得唔係食素既人批評呢d <br />\n好似50步笑100步咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會食肉，並尊重所有成為我食物既生命，唔會浪費。<br />\n而片中條友係玩弄緊生命，製造無意義既死亡。</blockquote><br />\n如果隻牛/豬果類 正常用來食既動物<br />\n就算你唔食 佢都要死